TITLE: Configuring Redux Provider in React Application Entry Point
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up the Redux Provider component in the main entry point of a React application. It wraps the root App component with Provider, passing the Redux store to make it accessible throughout the component tree.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reduxjs/redux/blob/master/docs/tutorials/essentials/part-2-app-structure.md#2025-04-07_snippet_24

LANGUAGE: TSX
CODE:
```
import React from 'react'
import { createRoot } from 'react-dom/client'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'

import App from './App'
import { store } from './app/store'

