TITLE: Slice Reducer Composition for Normalized Data in Redux
DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive approach using slice reducers to manage different parts of the state. This example shows action creators and multiple reducers working together to add a comment to a post in normalized form.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reduxjs/redux/blob/master/docs/usage/structuring-reducers/UpdatingNormalizedData.md#2025-04-07_snippet_1

