TITLE: Implementing Server-Side Rendering with Redux in Node.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up server-side rendering using Redux and React. It includes parsing request parameters, creating a Redux store, rendering React components to strings, and sending the pre-rendered page to the client.
